sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant AppController as AppWrapper Controller
    participant Resources as Wrapped Resources

    Note over User,Resources: Flow 2: AppWrapper Scheduling with Kueue

    User->>K8sAPI: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate AppWrapper<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation OK
    K8sAPI-->>User: Created

    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AppController->>K8sAPI: Watch AppWrapper status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AppController->>K8sAPI: Create wrapped resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI->>Resources: Deploy resources
